{"type": "article", "id": 13160, "title": "隐形音箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-07T07:28:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145943Fr5CSQ8Y6skD3Wb2.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦印象品牌 Vifa 近日推出了一套看上去完全不像音箱的音箱。这套看起来异常低调的名叫“斯得哥尔摩”，而和名字一样，这套音箱满满全是瑞士风格。音箱采用无线设计，可以自由摆放而免遭繁复的线材的困扰，目前在颜色上有红色，沙黄色，蓝色等不同选择，可以根据家居环境找到自己满意的选择。音箱售价 1499 欧元（约合 10100 元人民币），这是<a href=\"http://www.vifa.dk/shop/stockholm/c-24/p-116\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140802I81r4qpsawEti2M0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140803R5fCk1Db3SHBcW4h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140804zsGhaFbloHVK6R4N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140804XMZTLH2ifoOGdCjK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66623037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140805sf2HNigAXedFpWIB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}